#: templates/aboutus.html:8
msgid "To the men and women of Newport"
msgstr "I ddynion a menywod Casnewydd"

#: templates/aboutus.html:9
msgid "Did you know that around 22 men were shot\n"
"dead on a Newport street in 1839? They\n"
"were Chartists. They were demonstrating for\n"
"freedoms we take for granted today."
msgstr "Oeddech chi'n gwybod bod tua 22 o ddynion wedi'u saethu\n"
"ac wedi marw ar stryd yng Nghasnewydd ym 1839? Maent\n"
"yn Siartwyr. Roeddent yn arddangos dros\n"
"rhyddid a gymerwn yn ganiataol heddiw."

#: templates/aboutus.html:14
msgid "The Newport story starts in 1839 when thousands of\n"
"working men gathered in the South Wales Valleys\n"
"and marched on Newport through a cold and wet\n"
"November night. The exact motives for the march\n"
"are debatable. Some, including John Frost, were\n"
"protesting about the injustices and asking for the\n"
"release of fellow Chartists. Others were intent on\n"
"creating an uprising."
msgstr "Mae stori Casnewydd yn cychwyn ym 1839 pan ymgasglodd miloedd o\n"
"dynion sy'n gweithio yng Nghymoedd De Cymru\n"
"a gorymdeithio ar Gasnewydd trwy annwyd a gwlyb\n"
"Noson Tachwedd. Yr union gymhellion ar gyfer yr orymdaith\n"
"yn ddadleuol. Roedd rhai, gan gynnwys John Frost, yn\n"
"protestio am yr anghyfiawnderau a gofyn am y\n"
"rhyddhau cyd-Siartwyr. Roedd eraill yn benderfynol\n"
"creu gwrthryfel."

#: templates/aboutus.html:25
msgid "Chartism a national movement trying to improve the\n"
"living and working conditions for all through\n"
"Parliamentary Reform."
msgstr "Mudiad cenedlaethol oedd Siartiaeth yn ceisio gwella'r\n"
"amodau byw a gweithio i bawb drwyddo\n"
"Diwygio Seneddol."

